RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT Port.Name AS 'Port Name', Host.Name AS 'Host Name', Dhcpv4BlockConfig.BlockState AS 'State', Dhcpv4BlockResults.ElapsedTime AS 'Elapsed Time (seconds)', Dhcpv4BlockResults.CurrentAttemptCount AS 'Currently Attempting', Dhcpv4BlockResults.CurrentIdleCount AS 'Currently Idle', Dhcpv4BlockResults.CurrentBoundCount AS 'Currently Bound', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TotalAttemptCount AS 'Total Attempted', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TotalBoundCount AS 'Total Bound', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TotalFailedCount AS 'Total Failed', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TotalRetriedCount AS 'Total Retried', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TotalRenewedCount AS 'Total Renewed', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TotalRebootedCount AS 'Total Init-Rebooted', Dhcpv4BlockResults.BindRate AS 'Bind Rate (sessions/sec)', Dhcpv4BlockResults.AttemptRate AS 'Attempt Rate (sessions/sec)', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TxDiscoverCount AS 'Discover Tx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.RxOfferCount AS 'Offer Rx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TxRequestCount AS 'Request Tx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TxRenewCount AS 'Renew Tx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TxRebindCount AS 'Rebind Tx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TxRebootCount AS 'Init-Reboot Tx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.RxAckCount AS 'ACK Rx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TxReleaseCount AS 'Release Tx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.RxNakCount AS 'NAK Rx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.RxForceRenewCount AS 'Force Renew Rx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.TxDnav4RequestCount AS 'DNAv4 Request Tx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.RxDnav4ReplyCount AS 'DNAv4 Reply Rx Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.Dnav4RetryCount AS 'DNAv4 Retry Count', Dhcpv4BlockResults.Dnav4FailedCount AS 'DNAv4 Failed Count' FROM Host, Port, Dhcpv4BlockConfig, Dhcpv4BlockResults, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = Host.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND Dhcpv4BlockConfig.ParentHnd = Host.Handle AND Dhcpv4BlockResults.ParentHnd = Dhcpv4BlockConfig.Handle AND Host.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Dhcpv4BlockConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Dhcpv4BlockResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId )
